title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Volumes
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the base volumes of a Dell PowerVault ME5 system: volume health,
 whether the current owning controller matches the preferred owner, and the
 allocated size. Optional upper levels on the thin-provisioned fill ratio are
 available and off by default.

 Snapshots are volumes on the ME5 but are not shown here; they are covered by
 the "Dell PowerVault ME5: Snapshots" check.

 State is taken from the volume health value reported by the array. Conditions
 are configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5 volume" ruleset.

item:
 The volume name.

discovery:
 One service is created per base volume.
